---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="AI Search Visibility Guides, Glossary & Tools | Rank4AI" description="Learn about AI search visibility. Free guides, 50+ term glossary, AI visibility tools and 219 answered questions from Rank4AI.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-tag">Learn</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Learn</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-12 max-w-[700px]">Everything you need to understand AI search visibility. Guides, glossary, tools, and 219 answered questions.</p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <a href="/learn/guides/" class="card group">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Guides</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">In-depth guides covering AI search visibility, GEO, ChatGPT optimisation and more.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/learn/glossary/" class="card group">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Glossary</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">50+ AI search terms explained in plain English.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/learn/tools/" class="card group">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Free Tools</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">AI Visibility Checker and llms.txt Generator.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/learn/questions/" class="card group lg:col-span-3">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">AI Search Questions – 219 Answered</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">The most comprehensive library of AI search visibility questions and answers anywhere online.</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <h2 class="mt-16 mb-6">Featured Guides</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <a href="/learn/guides/complete-guide-ai-search/" class="card group">
        <h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Complete Guide to AI Search Visibility</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Everything you need to know about how AI search works and how to build visibility.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/learn/guides/geo/" class="card group">
        <h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">The Master Guide to GEO</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Generative Engine Optimisation explained. What it is, how it works, and what to do about it.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/learn/guides/get-cited-chatgpt/" class="card group">
        <h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">How to Get Cited by ChatGPT</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Practical strategies for getting your business cited in ChatGPT answers.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-24 px-10 mt-16">
    <a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
